<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fond-adj">fond <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fɒnd/    美 /fɑːnd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>喜爱的；爱好的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'<strong>m fond of</strong> English and do well in both speaking and writing.
我喜欢英语，擅长说和写。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She had <strong>grown fond of</strong> cooking.
她渐渐喜欢上了烹饪。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>深情的；温情的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a fond look / farewell
慈爱的目光/深情的道别</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
